Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那麼想要那顆紅色石頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就為了…那麼無聊的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 菲莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了 宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:00:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 我聽你媽媽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很喜歡咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了不要就是不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要媽媽的咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:56.15,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,650)\blur5\pos(440,1060)}想要傳達的{\1cBCE347}心{\1cFFFFFF}意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:29.61,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}眩しい光が土を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:35.36,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そう　そのたねは十分に芽を伸ばせる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:46.12,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}冷たい雨にも　強い風にも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:50.53,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何者でも揺るがない魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.91,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕らの背を押すわけはなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:58.63,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そう　くじけそうになった日もあっただろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:02.42,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不思議な力あふれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:09.15,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}愛の指す方へ　駆け出す少年のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:13.97,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}長い冬越え　僕ら包む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:18.34,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}春の息吹　福音になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:22.74,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}僕は君を探し求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:27.19,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}この日をずっと待ち続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:31.54,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}信じることの強さをそれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:35.95,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}それはいつかの孤独を癒すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:42.00,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}あぁ　もしも君が星に帰れと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:47.03,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}新しいたねをまこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:29.61,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}耀眼的光芒照亮大地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:35.36,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}含苞之種由此茁壯成長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:46.12,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}無論是冰冷的雨水  還是強勁的烈風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:50.53,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}這是誰都無法動搖的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.91,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}助我們一臂之力的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:58.63,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}曾經也有灰心喪氣的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:02.42,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不可思議的力量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:09.15,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}朝著愛的方向奔跑吧  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:13.97,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}跨越長冬  將我們包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:18.34,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}春天的氣息  成為福音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:22.74,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我追尋著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:27.19,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一直等待今天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:31.54,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}堅信著信任這一強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:35.95,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不久它便會治癒你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:42.00,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如果你將回歸繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:47.03,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}去播撒新的種子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙一直有挺冷淡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 你還在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的宗吾 不能和爸爸吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙他不是我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙他…是我已經離世的母親的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把無依無靠的我 硬是領養過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是完全不懂怎麼照顧孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做飯和洗衣服也根本不會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩什麼的做得難吃死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟媽媽做的咖哩完全沒法比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼 之後該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是回靛藍花園去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是去追宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼你們回去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢下我别管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管宗吾能不能救菲莉雅 他都不會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和多蒙鬧成那樣 也沒法回咖啡店了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 他們倆不是一起獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是共同遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真悶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想快點換班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟 不好意思 從車上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密碼被停用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過能走到這已經很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒空選擇其他手段了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…上了年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集了這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是知道我們要來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙說得一點也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對會把菲莉雅帶到祭壇去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是多蒙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要交給他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我約好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了要跟多蒙和好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險哞！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哞！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是之前的雙足機甲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也確認到利瑪和另外一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有兩個人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全機 建立包圍網！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次不能再讓他們逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決不允許第二次失敗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許動！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支援炮擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧托！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出發了 快準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 是要回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 去追宗吾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都把我們丢下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼還要管那種傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為他是那種傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不揍他一頓就不能消氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不巧 長官大人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我轉告他嗎 我在洋紅那邊的紀念墓地等他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不放他出包圍網
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝利遲早是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别讓他有喘息的機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堵住退路！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉！那傢伙是隊長機！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加斯 你他媽個分隊跑來幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出來 多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別想把我丢在一邊自己退休
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的戰爭現在才剛剛開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見 愛娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾…你兒子已經十四歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗馬上也要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我把他叫出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 可都當上了執行長官了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是政府的實質頭頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言出必行 真是了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 我就是有事想求他幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 堂堂長官大人辦這點事易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想讓那邊别再攻擊宗吾他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是謝謝你了 喚起了我的血性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 我現在找的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在的吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼在哪兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的目標是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把他引到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅你直接去祭壇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建議你…注意下背後！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得我卑鄙？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾 發射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙那是求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴你 所謂戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要贏了就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教會我這麼做的可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 找到利瑪囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放開利瑪也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 你得把多蒙叫到這來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是開學典禮的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這張是我們第一次一起做咖哩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那咖哩真是好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒吃過那麼香的咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.91,0:14:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會認識多蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙是我的師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們倆一起大開殺戒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是屠光了一個城也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把多蒙叫過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他搶先一步潛入政府裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛入政府？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次和宗吾吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…因為我沒有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直沒有和他吵過架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾他 會不會討厭我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想被宗吾討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最愛宗吾了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經像利刃一般的多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你弄得變成了鈍刀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起你這樣的人 我才更瞭解多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社蒙沒有變弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是變溫柔了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小鬼懂什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:10.90,injp,,0,0,0,,Story of Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.20,injp,,0,0,0,,Ready to shine baby
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.56,injp,,0,0,0,,Story of Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:14.94,injp,,0,0,0,,Ready for the new world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.30,injp,,0,0,0,,Story of Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.60,injp,,0,0,0,,Ready to shine baby
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:18.96,injp,,0,0,0,,Story of Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.34,injp,,0,0,0,,Ready for the new world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是多蒙嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:25.96,injp,,0,0,0,,のぞき込む　あなたの瞳に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:30.80,injp,,0,0,0,,「世界」が在る 気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:36.32,injp,,0,0,0,,深呼吸 している みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:42.18,injp,,0,0,0,,生まれ　変わる　予感が　したの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.94,injp,,0,0,0,,つぼみは咲き　果実になる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.31,injp,,0,0,0,,無邪気なまま　やがて熟れる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:52.49,injp,,0,0,0,,知らぬままに　夢のままに　落ちてく
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:55.20,injp,,0,0,0,,知りたくなる　解きたくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.70,injp,,0,0,0,,苦しくなる　泣きたくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.70,injp,,0,0,0,,止められない　逃げられない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:05.36,injp,,0,0,0,,―アイシテル―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:12.59,injp,,0,0,0,,解き放て　想いの翼で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:17.05,injp,,0,0,0,,未体験の　世界さえも　超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:22.77,injp,,0,0,0,,目醒めさせて　本当の私を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:30.92,injp,,0,0,0,,自由へと　誘って　その手で　Ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.28,injp,,0,0,0,,Story of Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.58,injp,,0,0,0,,Ready to shine baby
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:34.94,injp,,0,0,0,,Story of Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:36.32,injp,,0,0,0,,Ready for the new world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:42.41,injp,,0,0,0,,悲しみの　結び目をほどく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:47.16,injp,,0,0,0,,やさしい手に　触れたら　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:52.67,injp,,0,0,0,,無情にも　運命(さだめ)は　輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:50.04,injp,,0,0,0,,(どうして)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:59.59,injp,,0,0,0,,それは　とても　果敢ない　サヨナラ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:09.77,injp,,0,0,0,,命を　つないで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.68,injp,,0,0,0,,(星が星を　照らすように)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:09.77,injp,,0,0,0,,(愛が愛を　導くなら)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:12.30,injp,,0,0,0,,私はもう　負けたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:14.98,injp,,0,0,0,,進化してく　加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:17.56,injp,,0,0,0,,終わりじゃない　別れじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:22.71,injp,,0,0,0,,―シンジテル―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:29.61,injp,,0,0,0,,惹かれあう　瞳を見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:34.28,injp,,0,0,0,,未完成な　こころは　高鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:39.93,injp,,0,0,0,,身を焦がして　光よ　貫け
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:49.06,injp,,0,0,0,,遥かな　無重力の　彼方へ　Ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:00.78,injp,,0,0,0,,Story of Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.08,injp,,0,0,0,,Ready to shine baby
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.44,injp,,0,0,0,,Story of Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:04.82,injp,,0,0,0,,Ready for the new world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:11.83,injp,,0,0,0,,始まりと　終りの　向こうで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:16.17,injp,,0,0,0,,新たな　歴史が　生まれる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:22.14,injp,,0,0,0,,解き放て　想いの翼で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:26.60,injp,,0,0,0,,未体験の　世界さえも　超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:32.60,injp,,0,0,0,,目醒めさせて　本当の私を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:37.73,injp,,0,0,0,,自由へと　誘って　その手で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:45.74,injp,,0,0,0,,遥かな　無重力の　彼方へ　Ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:46.78,injp,,0,0,0,,Story of Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.08,injp,,0,0,0,,Ready to shine baby
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.44,injp,,0,0,0,,Story of Lucifer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:50.82,injp,,0,0,0,,Ready for the new world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦洛夫家長男 羅曼・瓦洛夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管家 奧托．莫托！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅曼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們休想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚐嚐這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了 我的小姐不見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑…跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慌什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲莉雅交給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙明明都在乎著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我的關注勝過任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉 回答我莫拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借給我力量吧 莫拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把它變成你的棺材！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 你搞什麼哞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫拉 你還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 速度力量都遠非剛才可比…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾這孩子可帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是要保護他的女人 成了個男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會輸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不能輸給你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我輸了 多蒙的這十年就被否定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺間 就長成了大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能輸給你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許你亂講多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保護好了她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 為什麼妳會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放不下妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我也有話想跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾成為個好男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用再擔心他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來得真慢啊 宗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:23.09,injp,,0,0,0,,あの日と同じ匂いはいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:29.05,injp,,0,0,0,,記憶を呼び起こしてしまうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:34.89,injp,,0,0,0,,それは甘く切ない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:40.82,injp,,0,0,0,,遠い記憶の中のあなたは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:46.70,injp,,0,0,0,,いつも微笑みかけてくれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:52.95,injp,,0,0,0,,ずっとそばにいれたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:58.54,injp,,0,0,0,,伝え切れない想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:04.67,injp,,0,0,0,,堰を切って溢れ出した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:11.89,injp,,0,0,0,,あなたがここにいないことに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:16.69,injp,,0,0,0,,とりとめなく気がつけば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:26.86,injp,,0,0,0,,とめどもなく涙が流れていたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:23.09,incn,,0,0,0,,和那天一樣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:29.05,incn,,0,0,0,,總會喚起那段記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:34.89,incn,,0,0,0,,香甜的 憂傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:40.82,incn,,0,0,0,,塵封在記憶深處的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:46.70,incn,,0,0,0,,總會對我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:52.95,incn,,0,0,0,,如果能一直在你身邊該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:58.54,incn,,0,0,0,,傳遞不盡的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:04.67,incn,,0,0,0,,像潮水一般湧出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:11.89,incn,,0,0,0,,你卻已經不再
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:16.69,incn,,0,0,0,,思緒萬千回過神來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:26.86,incn,,0,0,0,,早已停不住地淚流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩的食譜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多蒙他想重現母親的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果失敗了一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後做出那個味道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望那位大人還能暫且保持孤獨之身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途的終點 矗立著起始的門扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推開大門 那之後等待著眾人的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.20,0:23:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集「彗星．路西法」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深淵祭壇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起來拿上通往冒險的車票哞！
